Key files changed include fork anchoring in `packages/node/src/createTevmNode.js`, fork tag verification in `packages/state/src/actions/resolveForkBlockTag.js`, RPC selector fixes in `packages/actions/src/eth/*`, fork reset rebuilding in `packages/actions/src/internal/resetForkState.js`, and removal of the stale transport wrapper in `setupPrefetchProxy.js`.
